post_text:
From Dr. Bacha at NBHS;

I am happy to inform you that for the second time in a row one of our girls has won the Girls In Technology 2018 essay contest. Meriam Kamerji a North Bergen High School sophomore and a member of the computer club will receive a prize and will have the opportunity to recite her speech at the Girls in Technology symposium in front of 200 girls from different schools in the county. on March 29 at the Hudson County Community College. Please join me to congratulate Meriam Kamarji for this great achievement.

Great Job!!!

